Talkie MLX
Copyright 2026 Dhvanil Patel

This project provides an unofficial MLX implementation and conversion tools
for the Talkie-1930 model family.

Talkie-1930 is developed by the Talkie LM authors and distributed separately
at https://github.com/talkie-lm/talkie and https://huggingface.co/talkie-lm.
This repository does not include Talkie model weights.

Portions of the model architecture are based on the public Talkie PyTorch
implementation. The MLX-LM custom-model integration follows public mlx-lm
extension patterns.
